Introduction

Welcome to ArtShare. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you interact with our application. By using ArtShare, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection

We collect information primarily to provide and improve our service. The types of information we may collect include:

- User-Generated Content: Images or text you choose to share via our application for the purpose of posting to Pinterest.
- Pinterest Account Information: Your Pinterest username and any content information necessary for the applicationâ€™s functionalities.

Use of Information

Your information is used to:

- Provide and maintain our service, including to monitor the usage of our service.
- Allow you to participate in interactive features of our application when you choose to do so.
- Provide customer support.
- Detect, prevent, and address technical issues.
- Sharing of Information

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except:

- As required by law.
- To provide and maintain our service.
- To protect the rights or property of ArtShare.

Data Security

We are committed to protecting your data. We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information.

Children's Privacy

Our service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

